import React from 'react' import { Icon, Label, Menu, Table, Container, Tab } from 'semantic-ui-react' const TableData = ({stats, events}) => { let data = stats[0] ? stats.length : "none" return ( Date Hour Impressions Clicks Revenue POI ID {data["date"]} {data["hour"]} {data["impressions"]} {data["clicks"]} {data["revenue"]} {data["poi_id"]}
); } export default TableData;
